w.nikkansports.com/entertainment/news/f-et-tp0-20140526-1307344.html |script-title=ja:元ＡＫＢ大堀恵「本当に心が苦しい」 |language=ja |publisher=日刊體育 |date=2014-05-26 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527215658/http://www.nikkansports.com/entertainment/news/f-et-tp0-20140526-1307344.html |archivedate=2014-05-27 }}</ref>、[[森杏奈|森杏奈]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://twitter.com/_morianna/status/470547481344757761|title=森杏奈的推文|language=ja|publisher=森杏奈的[[推特|推特]]|date=2014-05-25|accessdate=2014-05-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528103407/https://twitter.com/_morianna/status/470547481344757761|archivedate=2014-05-28}}</ref>和[[秋元才加|秋元才加]]均表示擔心<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.mynavi.jp/news/2014/05/28/004/ |script-title=ja:元AKB・秋元才加、安心して臨める握手会を切望「二度と起こしてはいけない」 |language=ja |publisher={{Link-ja|Mynavinews|マイナビニュース}} |date=2014-05-28 |accessdate=2014-05-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528011119/http://news.mynavi.jp/news/2014/05/28/004/ |archivedate=2014-05-28 }}</ref>，另一前成員[[板野友美|板野友美]]則表示無法原諒兇徒的行為<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2037942/full/ |script-title=ja:元AKB板野友美、握手会事件に怒り「本当に許せません」 |language=ja |publisher=Oricon |date=2014-05-28 |accessdate=2014-05-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529062642/http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2037942/full/ |archivedate=2014-05-29 }}</ref>。

